    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926>
    bibo:endPage "42" ;
    bibo:journal "Subterranean Biology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2021-12-10" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "41" ;
    dc:creator "Nilsai 1, Areeruk; Detcharoen 1, Matsapume; Godeiro 2, Nerivania Nunes; Jantarit 3, Sopark" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Four new species of troglomorphic Coecobrya Yosii, 1956 (Collembola, Entomobryidae) from Thailand based on morphological and molecular evidence, with an updated key of Thai troglomorphic species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure4> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. The distribution map of the troglomorphic Coecobrya in Thailand and the habitus of the four new species. (1) A Coecobrya whitteni sp. nov. (2) B C. troglobia sp. nov. (3) C C. ellisi sp. nov. (4) D C. phitsanulokensis sp. nov. (5) C. chumphonensis Zhang & Nilsai, 2017 (6) C. sirindhornae Jantarit, Satasook & Deharveng, 2019 (7) C. polychaeta Zhang & Nilsai, 2017 and (8) C. cavicta Nilsai & Zhang, 2017. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/621479" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Coecobrya whitteni sp. nov. A Ventro-distal complex of labrum B Outer maxillary lobe C Labial palp D Ant. III organ E Chaetae of labial basis and ventral chaetotaxy of head F Mucro G Distal part of tita III and claw complex H Prelabral and labral chaetae I Mandibles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/621480" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Coecobrya whitteni sp. nov., continued A Distal part of manubrium ventrally B Trochanteral organ C Posterior side of ventral tube and Lateral flap D Dorsal cephalic chaetotaxy E Anterior side of ventral tube F Manubrium plaque G Clypeal chaetae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/621481" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.41.76926.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Coecobrya whitteni sp. nov., continued A Chaetotaxy of dorsal Th. II- III B Chaetotaxy of dorsal Abd. I- III C Chaetotaxy of dorsal Abd. IV D Chaetotaxy of dorsal Abd. V." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/621482" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

